<item>
            <title>[LU-6073] lustre/tests/*.c should use sys/xattr.h rather than attr/xattr.h</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-6073</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;In lustre/tests/&lt;/p&gt;
{multiop,orphan_linkea_check}
&lt;p&gt;.c we should include sys/xattr.h (provided by glibc-headers) rather than attr/xattr.h (provided by libattr-devel) since the former is more likely to be installed and has all of the needed declarations.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
