                            <comment id="102360" author="bogl" created="Mon, 29 Dec 2014 16:00:01 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Just as a data point I had builds fail on several of my long time builder VMs due to this issue.  I had not installed the libattr-devel rpms everywhere which contains the /usr/include/attr files.  They were never needed before the mod using &amp;lt;attr/xattr.h&amp;gt; landed in master.  While the problem went away as soon as I did install the additional rpm I agree that it would be preferable to use the more commonly available &amp;lt;sys/xattr.h&amp;gt; instead.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
